{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Pay parents that have to take time off due to school covid closures",
        "additional_details": "At the moment if our children\u2019s schools are closed due to a covid outbreak we aren\u2019t entitled to any SSP, furlough etc creating financial difficulties for parents. I believe seen as schools are to remain open that it is only fair that we receive some type of pay in this situation. It is well known that schools are highly affected by covid and as such many are having to close due to outbreaks. Please promise some help to parents in this situation.",
        "background": "Pay parents that have to take time off for dependant leave if their child\u2019s school is closed due to covid.",
